@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-4 p-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="display-5 text-center mb-4">About This Project</h1>

            <p class="lead text-dark">
                The <strong>Online Book Library System</strong> is a simple ASP.NET MVC web application designed to help users manage a collection of books efficiently.
                It supports basic operations like adding, viewing, editing, and deleting book records, with support for genre, availability, and publication year.
            </p>

            <p class="text-dark">
                This project was created as a capstone exercise for learning ASP.NET MVC concepts, including:
            </p>

            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                <li class="list-group-item">✔️ MVC architecture (Model-View-Controller)</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔️ Entity Framework Core and Code-First Migrations</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔️ CRUD operations with SQL database</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔️ Razor Views with Bootstrap styling</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔️ Simple authentication and UI logic</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="text-dark">
                The goal of this project is to simulate a real-world book inventory system while showcasing ASP.NET MVC skills.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
